text: Westminster is a city in northern Maryland, United States. It is a suburb of Baltimore. It is the seat of Carroll County. The city's population was 20,126 at the 2020 census. ==Famous People== Here are some famous people from Westminster: *Bill Oakley - television writer who worked on The Simpsons and Futurama ==References== Category:Cities in Maryland Category:County seats in Maryland
title: Westminster, Maryland
